#############################################################################################################################
#	How to run					sql_checker.pl -f <filename> -o <output_file> -e <error_file> [-h]	
#
#	Description					The program do multiple checks between the SQl code present in PCO code
#							and the actual Sql file.	
#
#	
#								variables
#	$file_content							the contents of file passed as input
#	$data_division_chunk						the part of cobol file where variables are declared
